      <p>In addition to their natural form, <a href="ch61s07.html#MonstersB-C40">bralanis</a> can assume the shape of a whirlwind or zephyr of dust, snow, or sand.</p>
      <p><a href="ch61s07.html#MonstersB-C40">Bralanis</a> speak Celestial, <a href="ch75.html#EpicMonsters(A-E)57">Infernal</a>, and Draconic, but can communicate with almost any creature, thanks to their <span class="emphasis"><em><a href="ch51.html#SpellsT-Z12">tongues</a></em></span> ability.</p>
      <div class="sect4" lang="en">
        <div class="titlepage">
          <div>
            <div>
              <h5 class="title"><a name="id1646335"/>Combat</h5>
